: 신경망이 학습하는 원리","seriesOrder":21},{"slug":"/ml/activation-functions/","title":"활성화 함수(Activation Functions): ReLU는 어떻게 딥러닝을 살렸나","seriesOrder":22},{"slug":"/ml/optimizers/","title":"옵티마이저(Optimizers): SGD에서 Adam까지, 경사하강법의 진화","seriesOrder":23},{"slug":"/ml/neural-network-tips/","title":"신경망 학습 안정화: Dropout, Batch Normalization, 가중치 초기화","seriesOrder":24}],"prevPost":{"slug":"/ml/gradient-descent/","title":"경사하강법(Gradient Descent): 비용 함수의 바닥을 찾아가는 알고리즘"},"nextPost":{"slug":"/ml/logistic-regression/","title":"로지스틱 회귀(Logistic Regression): 분류 문제의 시작점"}}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}